targets.expr:
sum(
    (increase(prometheus_sd_azure_refresh_failures_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0))
    +
    (increase(prometheus_sd_consul_rpc_failures_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0))
    +
    (increase(prometheus_sd_dns_lookup_failures_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0))
    +
    (increase(prometheus_sd_ec2_refresh_failures_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0))
    +
    (increase(prometheus_sd_gce_refresh_failures_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0))
    +
    (increase(prometheus_sd_marathon_refresh_failures_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0))
    +
    (increase(prometheus_sd_openstack_refresh_failures_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0))
    +
    (increase(prometheus_sd_triton_refresh_failures_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0))
    +
    (increase(prometheus_sd_file_read_errors_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0))
    +
    (increase(prometheus_sd_kuma_fetch_failures_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0))
    +
    (prometheus_sd_failed_configs{instance="$node"} or vector(0))
)

sum(
    (increase(prometheus_target_scrapes_exceeded_body_size_limit_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0))
    + 
    (increase(prometheus_target_scrapes_exceeded_sample_limit_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0))
    +
    (increase(prometheus_target_scrapes_sample_duplicate_timestamp_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0))
    +
    (increase(prometheus_target_scrapes_sample_out_of_bounds_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0))
    +
    (increase(prometheus_target_scrapes_exemplar_out_of_order_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0))
)

targets.expr:
sum(

    +
    increase(prometheus_tsdb_wal_truncations_failed_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0)
    +
    increase(prometheus_tsdb_wal_corruptions_total{instance="$node"}[$__range]) or vector(0)
)
